Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human? In this volume: children are missing and Queen Victoria is not happy.
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 7
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: A mysterious disease has turned a high school’s student body into zombies. In this volume: a zombie rampage at the airport.
Title: HIGH SCHOOL OF THE DEAD, VOL. 4
Author: Daisuke Sato and Shouji Sato
Contributor: by Daisuke Sato and Shouji Sato

Description: This series is about an incredibly positive young girl named Yotsuba. In this volume, she plays hide-and-seek with her father.
Title: YOTSUBA&!, VOL. 10
Author: Kiyohiko Azuma

Description: Maka, an arms expert, wants to turn the Soul Eater, her living scythe, into the ultimate weapon for Death.
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 7
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: Chi, a kitten with a nose for adventure, gets lost in the rain and must struggle to find food and shelter.
Title: CHI'S SWEET HOME, VOL. 7
Author: Konami Kanata

Description: Kraft Lawrence, a young merchant finds himself with a companion: Holo, the Wolf-God of the harvest.
Title: SPICE AND WOLF, VOL. 5
Author: Isuna Hasekura and Keito Koume
Contributor: by Isuna Hasekura and Keito Koume

Description: Oz, who is condemned for a mysterious sin, begins to learn more about the past.
Title: PANDORA HEARTS, VOL. 7
Author: Jun Mochizuki

Description: Nozomu is a teacher in Japan who is painfully depressed, but very popular with students.
Title: SAYONARA, ZETSUBOU-SENSEI, VOL. 11
Author: Koji Kumeta

Description: This series is about the son of a wine critic who must identify 12 wines in order to claim an inheritance.
Title: DROPS OF GOD, VOL. 1
Author: Tadashi Agi

Description: This small town is filled with intrigue and murder. In this volume, Rena Ryugu must come to terms with her father’s new lover.
Title: HIGURASHI WHEN THEY CRY, ATONEMENT ARC, VOL. 1
Author: Ryukishi07
